"{\"uid\": \"abc.net.au-news-2024-09-19-coast-rail-by-2032-olympics-embarrasment-104370920\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Personalise the news and  stay in the know  Emergency  Backstory  Newsletters  \\u4e2d\\u6587\\u65b0\\u95fb  BERITA BAHASA INDONESIA  TOK PISIN  Find any issues using dark mode?Please let us know  ABC Sunshine Coast  Topic:Rail Transport Industry  An artist impression of Direct Sunshine Coast rail.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BAHASA INDONESIA\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunshine_Coast_Region\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5642750508210585e-18, \"text\": \"Sunshine Coast\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunshine_Coast_Region\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunshine_Coast_Region\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied: Queensland Government)  Early work has begun on a direct rail line from Brisbane to the Sunshine Coast, planned for over 30 years.\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999998053681, \"rank\": 1.9461922707584672e-10, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However the joint state and federally funded stage one will only reach Caloundra by 2032.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.351707851570706e-34, \"text\": \"Caloundra\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The state opposition has promised a 100-day review to work out how to build the Sunshine Coast heavy rail line to Maroochydore by 2032, despite the government saying that is impossible.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.194479044429164e-37, \"text\": \"Maroochydore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Queensland opposition says the state will be embarrassed if the proposed Sunshine Coast direct rail line does not make it to the Maroochydore city centre by the 2032 Olympics.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"score\": 0.997257874681071, \"rank\": 0.0027496652458413604, \"text\": \"Queensland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.194479044429164e-37, \"text\": \"Maroochydore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nineteen kilometres of the spur line have been funded to finish at Caloundra by 2032as part of stage one, with the remaining 19km to Maroochydore yet to be funded or given a timeline.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 944, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.351707851570706e-34, \"text\": \"Caloundra\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\"}, {\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.194479044429164e-37, \"text\": \"Maroochydore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the LNP has promised a 100-day review of the 2032 Brisbane Olympics and Paralympic infrastructure.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1075, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2186804642471822e-46, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LNP leader David Crisafulli said Queenslanders did not want to be embarrassed by \\\"under investment\\\" on the international stage during the home Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2186804642471822e-46, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Crisafulli\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Crisafulli\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Crisafulli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Crisafulli\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do have a plan for generational infrastructure \\u2026 that looks like road and rail, but it also looks like having stadiums that Queenslanders can be proud of.\\\"\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An artist's impression of Beerwah station's upgrade on the Sunshine Coast ahead of the 2032 Olympic and Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beerwah_railway_station\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1703735645434863e-22, \"text\": \"Beerwah\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beerwah_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beerwah_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999592538795286, \"rank\": 2.8818126108438922e-05, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied, Transport and Main Roads)  Deputy Opposition leader Jarrod Bleijie said the 100-day review would work out how to build the full 38km Sunshine Coast heavy rail line from Beerburrum to Maroochydore by 2032, to ensure there is adequate transport for the region \\\"inclusive of the Mooloolah River Interchange, which is on the same transport corridor as that rail project\\\".\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jarrod_Bleijie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jarrod Bleijie\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jarrod_Bleijie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jarrod_Bleijie\"}, {\"begin\": 1792, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beerburrum_railway_station\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.141991833178376e-32, \"text\": \"Beerburrum\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beerburrum_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beerburrum_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mooloolah_River\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mooloolah River\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mooloolah_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mooloolah_River\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This would mean the line would go directly through Mr Bleijie's electorate of Kawana.\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Kawana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.765454784620162e-17, \"text\": \"Kawana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Kawana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Kawana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Labor Member for Caloundra Jason Hunt says the LNP held his seat for the past century and did not deliver on its infrastructure promises.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.403386577620439e-18, \"text\": \"Labor\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 2096, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.351707851570706e-34, \"text\": \"Caloundra\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\"}, {\"begin\": 2106, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason\", \"score\": 0.9816688248892246, \"rank\": 0.016338803021406913, \"t