2740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2480, \"end\": 2488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999999731699, \"rank\": 2.677944291103768e-11, \"text\": \"ABC News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9349427832137848, \"rank\": 0.06958329562900846, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 2498, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"score\": 0.999999965642474, \"rank\": 3.43395482606043e-08, \"text\": \"Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\"}, {\"begin\": 2510, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2186804642471822e-46, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Adding in today's announcements, the LNP already have a more than $7.65 billion black hole.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2778, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2186804642471822e-46, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's just on the Sunshine Coast.\\\"\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rail Back on Track spokesperson Brian O'Connor said despite the delays the rail line had to make it to Maroochydore.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2907, \"end\": 2921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\", \"score\": 0.6683398713883423, \"rank\": 0.36315789473679255, \"text\": \"Brian O'Connor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\"}, {\"begin\": 2978, \"end\": 2990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.194479044429164e-37, \"text\": \"Maroochydore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The issue is when?\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know that the line will get to Caloundra and, in a pinch if the money is forthcoming, to Birtinya,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3047, \"end\": 3056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.351707851570706e-34, \"text\": \"Caloundra\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\"}, {\"begin\": 3105, \"end\": 3113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birtinya,_Queensland\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Birtinya\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birtinya,_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birtinya,_Queensland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian O'Connor from Rail Back on Track said the rail line would be most effective when it reached Maroochydore.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3126, \"end\": 3140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\", \"score\": 0.6683398713883423, \"rank\": 0.36315789473679255, \"text\": \"Brian O'Connor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\"}, {\"begin\": 3224, \"end\": 3236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.194479044429164e-37, \"text\": \"Maroochydore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied: Brian O'Connor)  \\\"A bus network could radiate out from [Caloundra station] to serve other parts of the Sunshine Coast as an interim measure.\\\"\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3248, \"end\": 3262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\", \"score\": 0.6683398713883423, \"rank\": 0.36315789473679255, \"text\": \"Brian O'Connor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_O'Connor_(baseball_coach)\"}, {\"begin\": 3304, \"end\": 3313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.351707851570706e-34, \"text\": \"Caloundra\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caloundra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr O'Connor said the LNP commitment was only for a review of the project's time frame and not to build tracks to Maroochydore by the 2032 Olympics.\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3412, \"end\": 3415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2186804642471822e-46, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 3504, \"end\": 3516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.194479044429164e-37, \"text\": \"Maroochydore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The review is welcomed because it will confirm the urgency to build the line.\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know from the business case that 80 per cent of Sunshine Coast residents back construction of the direct Sunshine Coast line,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The section of track that is most in doubt is the bit from Maroochydore to the Sunshine Coast Airport.\\\"\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3819, \"end\": 3831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.194479044429164e-37, \"text\": \"Maroochydore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maroochydore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The LNP has announced $400 million for five projects to ease traffic congestion in and around problematic Caloundra Road.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3869, \"end\": 3872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2186804642471822e-46, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": 