pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenock_Morton_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 4200, \"end\": 4216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Crisafulli\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Crisafulli\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Crisafulli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Crisafulli\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC Sunshine Coast: Amy Sheehan)  \\\"We are mapping out a long-term vision to show we are fair dinkum and we are putting the money on the table to begin work immediately,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If elected, the party has promised to build an overpass, link road, and slip lanes to ease pressure on Caloundra Road.\", \"from\": 4433, \"to\": 4551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has also pledged to complete the long-awaited Third Avenue connection road, which would provide alternative access into the Caloundra CBD from the busy Nicklin Way.\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Third Ave plan to connect Nicklin Way to the Caloundra CBD.\", \"from\": 4722, \"to\": 4785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4752, \"end\": 4763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicklin_Way\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicklin Way\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicklin_Way\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicklin_Way\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied: Sunshine Coast Council)  Mr Hunt said Labor still had $7 million on the table for the 3rd Avenue project, but work had not progressed because the federal government withdrew its $7 million funding commitment.\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 5004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4796, \"end\": 4818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunshine_Coast_Region\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunshine Coast Council\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wiki